ded regions than the\ncool gas and, therefore, it is more likely to be detected along a generic line\nof sight.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Aug 2016 20:00:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 19 May 2017 23:58:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-06-28"}
